{"tid":1757620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民內閣] 請所有民主派區議員支持黃義工計劃","createTime":"2019-11-26T15:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T14:03:45.000Z","uid":185628,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5753e4d50dc8bef403b185817d5fba681d861aaa","tid":1757620,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"由於好多義工組織都係藍，所以我唔想做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃義工計劃絕對符合道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我驚獻世派拎credit---&gt;多人投建制---&gt;害死晒全香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n制度:<br />\n自由分組制，自己諗點樣服務社會，最後由討論區眾議+議員或助理批准，成為受民主派區議員認證嘅黃義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n此計劃有好多好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子:<br />\n手工製作d啱弱勢社群用嘅野/提供服務<br />\n好處包括:<br />\n1. 訓練手足團體行動能力(有益勇武及後勤)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 令公眾知道我地唔單止有破壞，亦有建設(文宣+和理非左膠最愛)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 打卡扮抗爭左(偽黃最愛)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 維穩(少左前線示威者)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 拉票"},{"pid":"68f821b7d368e084e1254ea0f0e16afb2649f91e","tid":1757620,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec9d55084918aad1bc3004f9de371f20c2c6bf43","tid":1757620,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4674598bbde1530be3d892d99056839cca5a6ca","tid":1757620,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713c446b23dff688d76c4dec174d73d8728c3a6f","tid":1757620,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0080e519d1f495f573af9b0ffc17980cf833819","tid":1757620,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:13:18.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有需要我可以幫手organize<br />\n<br />\n履歷:<br />\n曾在舊登籌辦數屆平安夜探訪露宿者之家/老人院活動"},{"pid":"14d7ae886251a1e43aca382db54dc4fd766267f2","tid":1757620,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}